s/weixintupian_20210224160842.jpg\">\n  \n  <div class=\"current wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n<div class=\"clearfix container\">\n    <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n航空宇航工程系</div>\n    <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk.htm\">师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\">师资信息</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx/hkyhgcx.htm\">航空宇航工程系</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szqk/ys.htm\" title=\"院士\">院士</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\" title=\"师资信息\">师资信息</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n<div>\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff;\">\n\n       <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/C/16/3A/DB182AE9CDD2ABC3A9D9FA1D4FE_2D4B138B_71F3.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>董戈</a></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                                    <p>职称：研究员</p>\n                                  \n                                    <p>E-mail address：dongge@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div> \n        <div id=\"vsb_content\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">个人简介</div><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p>董戈，工学博士Ph.D，清华大学航天航空学院研究员，博士生导师。<br></p>\n<p>主讲课程：航空宇航电子系统</p>\n<p>邮箱：<a href=\"mailto:dongge@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn\">dongge@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</a></p>\n</div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">教育背景</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>1990年考入清华大学电子工程系，同年由清华大学选派国家教育部公派留学苏联。</p>\n<p>1997年和2000年分别获俄罗斯国立莫斯科鲍曼技术大学工学硕士学位和工学博士学位。期间连续10年获中国教育部全优奖学金资助。1997获俄罗斯高教部全优毕业证书。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">工作履历</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>2000年8月至2013年1月</p>\n<p>中国科学院电子学研究所主要从事航空航天微波遥感和微波电子领域工作。2002年晋升为副研究员，2008年晋升为研究员。期间曾担任微波成像技术国家科技重点实验室副主任等职务。</p>\n<p>2013年1月至今 清华大学航天航空学院。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术兼职</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>中国科技部国际合作项目评审专家。</p>\n<p>圣彼得堡彼得大帝理工大学 客座教授2015-2018</p>\n<p>莫斯科国立鲍曼技术大学 客座教授 2016-2018</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">社会兼职</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>欧美同学会-中国留学人员联谊会理事</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究领域</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>微波遥感</p>\n<p>SAR-合成孔径雷达</p>\n<p>无人机电子系统</p>\n<p>航空航天微波电子组件、模块和系统</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究概况</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>航空航天微波电子和遥感领域具备理论基础坚实并具有丰富的工程开发经验。在国内首次提出了海洋微波遥感非穿透性探测方法并完成计算机仿真模拟及机载SAR设计与海陆空联合试验，在此基础上开展海洋探测星载SAR设计，解决了高辐射分辨率和超宽测绘带宽等关键技术，同时承担了中国首部千瓦级星载脉冲行波放大器的研制工作。</p>\n<p>航空航天电子系统和设备：新型航空航天电子和微波系统和设备的研制。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>2000年获中国科学院归国择优基金资助。</p>\n<p>2012年获清华大学优秀人才引进计划基金资助。</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术成果</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p>发表论文40余篇，获得专利1项。作为课题负责人完成了863计划项目2项、科工项目1项、国家级重点基金和基金项目2项、中科院基金项目1项。作为主要负责人之一参与了国家大型航天型号项目，中俄政府间重大国际合作项目等工作。</p>\n<p>[1] Ruoxing Ding; Dong Ge; Xiao Xi Research on Power Sharing Results Parameterization of Hybrid Energy Storage System 4th International Conference on Electrical Systems for Aircraft, Railway, Ship propulsion and Road Vehicles &amp; International Transportation Electrification Conference Proceedings, november 2-4, 2016</p>\n<p>[2] DONG Ge; Agulnik A B; MA Rui; SHA Minggong Analisisof Supersonic Business Jet Engine Technical Solution The 2016 Asia-Pacific International Symposium on Aerospace Technology OCTOBER 25-27, 2016</p>\n<p>[3] Tan Shucheng; Dong Ge; Zhang Hui; Zhi Na; Xiao Xi Virtual DC Machine Control Strategy of Energy Storage Converter in DC Microgrid 2016 IEEE Electric Power and Energy Conference Proceedings, October 12-14, 2016</p>\n<p>[4] Dong Ge; Hu, Boxiong Methods to Improve the Phase Stability of High-Power TWTA, 9th International Conference on Microwave and Millimeter Wave Technology Proceedings, v.1, p 150-152, June 5-8, 2016.</p>\n<p>[5] Hu, Boxiong; Dong Ge Analysis and simulation of a higher amplitude Expansion Millimeter Wave Predistortion Linearizer, 9th International Conference on Microwave and Millimeter Wave Technology Proceedings, v.1, p 123-125, June 5-8, 2016.</p>\n<p>[6] Burtsev S; Dong Ge Feasibility Analysis of Hydrogen Fuel Using for Short and Medium Range Aircrafts’ Engines Safety in Technosphere, v 5, n 2. p11-17, 2016. In Russian DOI: 10.12737/20791</p>\n<p>[7] Dong Ge; Chen Yu; Chen, Zhonglin; Xu Chenqian; Zhang Xuanli An EPC circuit reducing high voltage storage capacitance in pulse TWTA International Conference on Electric Information and Control Engineering, ICEICE 2011, p 3942-3945, April 15-17, 2011.</p>\n<p>[8] Tian Xin-Yuan; Dong Ge; Zhu Min-Hui Analysis of errors in waveform storage LFM generator design, Journal of Electronics and Information Technology, v 27, n 8, p 1240-1243, August 2005. In Chinese.</p>\n<p>[9] Dong Ge Corrected engineering estimation formula of radiometric resolution in SAR images Journal of Electronics and Information Technology, v 26, n 12, p1901-1907, December 2004. In Chinese.</p>\n<p>[10] Dong Ge Signal to noise ratio, number of multilook and image quality in SAR images, v 26, n SUPPL., p 365-368, September 2004. In Chinese.</p>\n<p>[11] Xiao Jiang; Dong Ge; Zhu Min Hui A novel aperture coupled microstrip antenna array with low cross-polarization, low sidelotoe and backlobe, 2004 4th International Conference on Microwave and Millimeter Wave Technology, p 223-226, August 18-21, 2004.</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">[12] Dong G; Zhu, MH; Tian, XY Reserch on some problems about SAR radiometric sesolution International Workshop on Wave Propagation, Scattering and Emission (WPSE 2003) Proceedings, p 45-50, Jun. 1-4, 2003.</p></div></div>\n\n     </div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"friends-box wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"friends-left\">友情链接</div>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1696534067, 71220)\">清华大学</a>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; anima